node.text:
-Hey Moody fam 🙋🏾‍♀️

We’ve partnered with our friends over @hexbrand, to showcase MG founder @so.shauna as one of the female creatives for their “Women in Focus” series. 

“This video gives you a look at my journey as a photographer. I share some of my experiences, challenges, and also some advice for my fellow female creatives. Photography might be a male dominated industry, but I’m happy to know there are women out there changing the narrative. A huge thank you to Hex Brand for letting me share my story. I’m honored to be selected as part of this project.”

Please tag/share this video with other female creatives who this might inspire. And check out the rest of their series featuring other talented female creatives!
Link:- http://hex.tw/3obXwPJ

Peace and Love ✌🏾♥️
